author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by LAN Party Adventures, a nostalgic single-player adventure that blends detective storytelling with a retro tech management simulator. – https://store.steampowered.com/app/3566720/LAN_Party_Adventures/

This week on Firelink, Marty, KC, and Nick chat about their favorite games from this year that didn't get the love they deserved, plus what they've been playing recently (spoilers, it's more Silksong.

Keep up to date on the standings of our Firelink Fantasy Critic Draft -- https://www.fantasycritic.games/league/6093c943-c06e-4f44-8206-157e410d7914/2025

If you dig the podcast, considering supporting us over at Patreon --  https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

Check out our excellent selection of merch over at our DFTBA store -- https://store.dftba.com/collections/second-wind

Snag yourself an Adventure is Nigh! plushie over at Shark Robot -- https://sharkrobot.com/collections/second-wind
title: Rad 2025 Games That Slipped Under the Radar | Firelink Podcast
